Title: Misbegotten
Plot: The explosion of a package including scientific research injures a pregnant security guard, leading to the investigation of the scientist's experiments.
GuestStars: Leigh Wade, Christy Baron, Thomas G. Waites, Matthew Lawler, Caitlin Muelder, Grant Shaud, Amy Landecker, Sherman Howard, Michael DeVries, Susanna Frazer, Nicole Alifante, Stephen Park, Peter Parros, Benim Foster
